cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.CL 

The paper describes a new convolutional neural network (CNN) for classifying 3D point clouds of urban or indoor scenes. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses solutions to problems encountered while working on scene point clouds, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with point classification, which could be categorized under graphics (cs.GR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
